415
00:37:51,510 --> 00:37:55,380
spirit alive in the next round of the FA cup.
Finally—[Interruption.]

416
00:37:55,380 --> 00:37:58,910
>>Mr Speaker: Order. The hon. Gentleman must
be heard.

417
00:37:58,910 --> 00:38:04,030
>>Paul Scully: Finally, will my right hon.
Friend join me in congratulating and thanking

418
00:38:04,030 --> 00:38:11,960
Arsenal for their generosity in allowing Sutton
to keep a little extra slice of the FA cup

419
00:38:11,960 --> 00:38:12,960
pie?

