429
00:39:02,809 --> 00:39:09,539
in Edinburgh, is being sold, and recent newspaper
reports suggest that the contract could be

430
00:39:09,539 --> 00:39:14,869
concluded soon. That is happening despite
the UK’s stated focus on research and development,

431
00:39:14,869 --> 00:39:20,670
and the fact that no realistic guarantees
have yet been given as to the continuation

432
00:39:20,670 --> 00:39:26,510
of a proper headquarters and board based in
