433
00:39:26,510 --> 00:39:33,762
to looking again at why a sale at this time
is not in the best interests of Edinburgh,

434
00:39:33,762 --> 00:39:35,940
the green agenda or UK taxpayers?

435
00:39:35,940 --> 00:39:41,670
>>The Prime Minister: Before I respond to
