Friend the Member for Sutton and Cheam introduced

439
00:40:00,410 --> 00:40:01,410
into the Chamber.

440
00:40:01,410 --> 00:40:04,410
The hon. Member for Edinburgh West (Michelle
Thomson) mentioned the Green Investment Bank.

441
00:40:04,410 --> 00:40:08,020
If I may, I will write to her with a response
